metadata.name: Tree 1
metadata.description:
The Floating Trees of Mœbdean is a collection of 12 pictures made with Stable Diffusion in November 2022. Each picture is unique and has never been seen anywhere else. 1536 x 2880 pixels.

The tree you'll buy is obviously, also, a symbol off something in life, growing, strong, elegant and powerful in a slow way...
